Definition: reduction to the absurd) a disproof by showing that the consequences of the proposition are absurd
Example: or a proof of a proposition by showing that its negation leads to a contradiction
Synonyms: reductio, disproof, reduction, to, the, absurd, a, by, showing, that, consequences, of, proposition, are, or, proof, its, negation, leads, contradiction
Category: noun.cognition
